---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Support — Rentar Fuel Catalyst | Rentar"
  description="Technical support for Rentar Fuel Catalyst customers. Installation guidance, troubleshooting, and ongoing assistance for authorized product owners."
>
  <section class="hero" style="min-height:35vh;">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-tag">Customer Support</p>
      <h1 style="font-size:2.6rem;">Support</h1>
      <p>Technical support for Rentar Fuel Catalyst customers. Our engineering team is available to assist authorized product owners with installation, operation, and troubleshooting.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="manifesto-block">
        <p>Rentar provides technical support to customers who have purchased genuine Rentar products through Rentar or an authorized distributor. Our support includes installation guidance, operational best practices, troubleshooting, and performance verification assistance.</p>

        <p class="highlight-label" style="font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);font-size:1.15rem;margin-top:32px;">Contact Support</p>
        <p>For technical support, contact our team at <a href="mailto:info@rentar.com" style="color:var(--orange);">info@rentar.com</a>. Please include your product details, installation date, and a description of your question or issue.</p>

        <p class="highlight-label" style="font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);font-size:1.15rem;margin-top:32px;">Verify Your Product</p>
        <p>If you are uncertain whether your Rentar Fuel Catalyst is genuine, contact us to verify. Only products purchased through Rentar or an authorized distributor are eligible for technical support and warranty coverage where applicable.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center; margin-top:48px;">
        <a href="mailto:info@rentar.com" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Support</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
